title: Dagger, ca. 1400–1500
creditline: The Robert L. Metzenberg Collection, gift of Eleanor L. Metzenberg
description: Long pointed blade, corroded. Curved rectangular guard. Tang ends in flat trefoil. Wooden scales (not original).
